    "name": "KYORA",
    "steam_appid": 3337850,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337850/extras/89acfdfa27b3ffe9adee17bccc563167.avif?t=1768818244\" width=780 height=380 /></span>‎ ‎ <br>本作由获奖无数的挖矿类沙盒游戏《护核纪元》原班人马打造，创新加入魔法元素，旨在为玩家带来眼前一亮的多人冒险体验……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >废都之间，每颗像素都是创造新事物的实用工具。挖掘宝贵资源，打造能够改变物理特性的魔杖，对抗强大头目的同时，不忘改造周边环境，逐步建立起专属基地。<br>‎  <br>‎ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337850/extras/7d23fed5e014a292dc7a97e060642f40.webp?t=1768818244\" width=600 height=42 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入自动生成的开放世界，处处都有意想不到的收获。上天入地，挖凿神奇魔法材料。打造能够操纵物质的魔杖，鸟枪换炮，挑战先驱守卫这种掌控自然、呼风唤雨的强大头目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337850/extras/b1b01b42fe089ba22215e5316a681d16.webp?t=1768818244\" width=600 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挥洒创意无需拘束，改造地形全靠像素。搭桥修路前往新区域，用地形像素材料捏出合你心意的基地。战斗中也想利用地形？使出能力，便可以造出平台和掩体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337850/extras/86dbd2adde5e71548e2dbaa773a672cf.webp?t=1768818244\" width=600 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《KYORA》的世界里埋藏了不少秘密，越是腹地，越有危险环伺。密林吞没废墟，酷热大漠飞沙走石，要想活下来，就得巧用每种生态环境中的资源。收集材料，打造强力武器和甲胄，播种之余还要研究配方，这都是你穿越荒野的底气……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337850/extras/eea64d9b57dc96ccbc88adb7ddbc3afd.webp?t=1768818244\" width=600 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >形单影只最危险！与好友同行，便可以强强联手，试出超有趣的魔杖能力组合技。本作最多支持 8 人合作游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337850/extras/ac0dc8729a4c80d41a72c92ca024635d.poster.avif?t=1768818244\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337850/extras/ac0dc8729a4c80d41a72c92ca024635d.webm?t=1768818244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
